  "title": "Admin Support  Cum Telemarketer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>This role is primarily administrative, supporting daily operations and coordination. You will also conduct recruitment-related calls using provided scripts, with opportunities to suggest improvements for better outcomes.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Enter data accurately and manage filing and document organization to support daily operations</li><li>Coordinate schedules and follow up on tasks to ensure smooth workflow</li><li>Deliver forms or documents as needed to support operational requirements</li><li>Conduct recruitment-related calls following provided scripts and engage candidates professionally</li><li>Track call outcomes and update records precisely to maintain accurate recruitment data</li><li>Provide constructive feedback and suggest script revisions to improve call effectiveness</li><li>Assist the team with various ad-hoc administrative tasks as required</li><li>Follow instructions carefully and maintain reliability in task completion</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Prior experience in administrative roles or telemarketing is advantageous but not required</li><li>Demonstrates strong verbal communication skills and confidence when engaging with strangers over the phone</li></ul>",
